It is apparent that the\ntraits of high ion absorption in a supershell, as well as the ionizing\nmechanisms responsible, can vary among sight lines through the shell.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Nov 2001 16:55:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
